    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The Gradle wrapper needs to be built. Try running <code>gradle wrapper --gradle-version 2.13</code>.</p>\n<p>Remember to change 2.13 to your Gradle version number. After running this command, you should see new scripts added to your project folder. You should be able to run the wrapper with <code>./gradlew build</code> to build your code.</p>\n<p>Please refer to this guide for more information: <em><a href=\"https://spring.io/guides/gs/gradle/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Building Java Projects with Gradle</a></em></p>\n"
