    "body" : "<h3>Linux and macOS</h3>\n<p>As noted in the comments, just running</p>\n<pre><code>./gradlew\n</code></pre>\n<p>worked for me. Adding the <code>./</code> tells it to look in the current directory since it isn't in the path.</p>\n<p>If it stills doesn't work, run (<em>as commented by Fadi</em>)</p>\n<pre><code>chmod +x gradlew\n</code></pre>\n<p>And then try again</p>\n<h3>Windows PowerShell</h3>\n<pre><code>.\\gradlew\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
