    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The same problem occurs to me...</p>\n<p>I check the file wrx permissions with:</p>\n<p><code>$ls -l ./gradlew</code> -&gt; -rw-rw-r-- (no execute permission)</p>\n<p>So I use command <code>$chmod +x ./gradlew</code> and this problem is solved.</p>\n"
