    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If the answer marked as correct does not work, it is because you need to identify yourself as a super user.</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-none prettyprint-override\"><code>sudo gradle wrapper --gradle-version 2.13\n</code></pre>\n<p>It worked for me.</p>\n"
