    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In addition to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/41700798/error-message-gradlew-command-not-found/43936928#43936928\">Suragch's answer</a>:</p>\n<p><strong>Linux and macOS</strong></p>\n<p><code>./gradlew clean</code></p>\n<p><strong>Windows PowerShell</strong></p>\n<p><code>.\\gradlew clean</code></p>\n<p><strong>Windows cmd</strong></p>\n<p><code>gradlew clean</code></p>\n"
